#: templates/registration/password_reset_form.html:7
msgid "Back to sign in"
msgstr "Späť na prihlásenie"

#: templates/registration/password_reset_done.html:14
msgid ""
"If an account exists for that address, we've sent a link to set your "
"password. It may take a minute to arrive."
msgstr ""
"Ak pre túto adresu existuje účet, poslali sme ti odkaz na nastavenie hesla. "
"Doručenie môže chvíľu trvať."

#: templates/registration/password_reset_email.html:1
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Hi,\n"
"\n"
"you can set your Compass password using the link below:\n"
"\n"
"%(protocol)s://%(domain)s%(reset_path)s\n"
"\n"
"Once it's set, sign in with your email (%(email)s) to reach your tournament "
"private links.\n"
"\n"
"If you didn't expect this email, you can safely ignore it.\n"
"\n"
"— Compass"
msgstr ""
"Ahoj,\n"
"\n"
"heslo do Compass si môžeš nastaviť cez tento odkaz:\n"
"\n"
"%(protocol)s://%(domain)s%(reset_path)s\n"
"\n"
"Keď ho nastavíš, prihlás sa svojím e-mailom (%(email)s) a dostaneš sa k "
"súkromným odkazom na svoje turnaje.\n"
"\n"
"Ak si tento e-mail nečakal, môžeš ho pokojne ignorovať.\n"
"\n"
"— Compass"

#: templates/registration/password_reset_email.html:13
#, python-format
msgid "How we handle your data: %(protocol)s://%(domain)s%(privacy_path)s"
msgstr "Ako spracúvame tvoje údaje: %(protocol)s://%(domain)s%(privacy_path)s"

#: templates/registration/password_reset_form.html:3
